{"tid":2417244,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"聲稱多次詢問記者補交資料不果 入境處被指誤導申訴專員致《蘋果》投訴失敗","createTime":"2021-02-21T17:06:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-21T21:23:27.000Z","uid":240362,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3c35bd94ef93dcb7fbef433489a66b88de0ac80e","tid":2417244,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T17:06:41.000Z","msg":"《蘋果》自前年起，就入境處突然收緊出生及結婚紀錄的查冊規定，向申訴專員公署投訴，其後入境處回覆公署，指傳媒可以公眾利益為由申請查冊，惟記者實測發現與事實不符，並再度向公署投訴。公署早前回覆投訴不成立，並引述入境處提供的資料，指該處曾多次詢問記者會否補交資料，惟根據本報記者紀錄，入境處從未就查冊目的及用途，要求記者補交資料；有前立法會議員批評入境處「講大話」誤導公署調查。《蘋果》記者已就此要求公署覆檢結果。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/RidywIdmYPyBoA8OQ-578ykzlXo=/802x818/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NBYCPOMN2RFHTLCBTMLIFIKDOE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FRidywIdmYPyBoA8OQ-578ykzlXo%3D%2F802x818%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNBYCPOMN2RFHTLCBTMLIFIKDOE.png&h=e4492063&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n入境處於2019年10月突然收緊「香港結婚紀錄」及「出生登記紀錄」的查冊安排，任何人若申請查閱他人的出生或結婚紀錄，須獲當事人授權，否則要提供合理原因供入境處審批。<br />\n<br />\n因上述做法涉剝奪新聞自由及公眾知情權，《蘋果》記者隨後向申訴專員公署投訴，入境處回覆公署時表示，傳媒可以涉及公眾利益為由，向該處提出翻查及索取第三者的出生登記或結婚紀錄。惟記者其後表明查冊目標人士為陌生人，目的為「核實二人夫妻關係」，用途是「新聞活動」，最終仍被入境處拒絕查冊申請，因此再度向公署投訴。<br />\n<br />\n公署早前回覆調查結果，指入境處拒絕是次申請，是因記者提供的資料，「並不能令該處充份信納其申請要求與設立香港結婚紀錄的目的相符」，以及理據不足以令該處豁免《私隱條例》的保障資料原則，又稱無證據顯示入境處刻意阻撓傳媒查冊，故認為投訴不成立。<br />\n<br />\n公署在報告中亦建議入境處，應盡量以實例向申請人闡明何謂充足的申請理據及文件，並要列明覆檢機制以提升透明度。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210222/G5JT4WILMBAPVMFI4UVN6VS5EU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210222%2FG5JT4WILMBAPVMFI4UVN6VS5EU%2F&d=nAM79WGQOJ1S2Ssbv1FDYy9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=ee373b49\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210222%2FG5JT4WILMBAPVMFI4UVN6VS5EU%2F&h=3e619a21\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210222/G5JT4WILMBAPVMFI4UVN6VS5EU/</a>"},{"pid":"322858c9a1cee56590ea3baba56e6234a08e4306","tid":2417244,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T17:09:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de3ee194606622d1522aaea473b0c77abb1e978a","tid":2417244,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T17:14:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b14219d5c52162f9bf324a65811fe18dc26fd4e4","tid":2417244,"uid":86509,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T17:16:05.000Z","msg":"恆之無效嘅投訴機制"},{"pid":"04a37afd4e26d3677ddbd4831ecb23edf3bec4bf","tid":2417244,"uid":53959,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T17:16:16.000Z","msg":"又係黑境"},{"pid":"ebd317c2a2f317de83a4dd70436b5bc40e3e7b6c","tid":2417244,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T17:22:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ca10b191256be6864b8203189e69269211901fd","tid":2417244,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T17:25:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e396b4261276ab2bb994b7a3144e210230a0047","tid":2417244,"uid":113000,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T17:58:37.000Z","msg":"遲下全部國家機密<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85c299f35840eb09821285d2fe359047c8e7ef6a","tid":2417244,"uid":302471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T19:10:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de5c6bc154b4f9cf9b7e6eab7f6c1ecf54cc7ec9","tid":2417244,"uid":6981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T20:19:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94788ddc0d2bcd0576e367b691e16d05c65ff88b","tid":2417244,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T20:20:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bab92f32267decdf94f2f590e80ec86565f89b8","tid":2417244,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T21:23:27.000Z","msg":"推"}]}